---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About" description="Learn about Vanessa Manear, certified disability representative and founder of SS Disability Associates, LLC.">
  <section class="bg-brand-900 text-white py-16 px-4 text-center">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">About</h1>
      <p class="text-brand-100 text-lg">Meet Vanessa Manear — certified disability representative and founder.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16 space-y-6 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
    <p>
      I am a certified disability representative and former Social Security employee, with more than three decades of knowledge
      and expertise in all types of Social Security matters. As founder and CEO of SS Disability Associates, LLC — an agency
      dedicated to assisting individuals in filing for Social Security disability benefits — I have assisted numerous individuals
      in obtaining benefits.
    </p>
    <p>
      As a former paralegal with Social Security, I have first-hand knowledge of the ever-changing policies and programs of
      the Administration, which has led to success in obtaining benefits for many individuals.
    </p>
    <p>
      I completed my undergraduate degree at the University of Alabama at Birmingham (UAB) and hold a BS degree. I am an active
      member of the National Association of Disability Representatives (NADR), networking with attorneys and disability advocates
      throughout the nation.
    </p>
    <p class="font-semibold text-brand-800">
      Obtaining Social Security benefits can be difficult and confusing — I can assist you in filing for all types of benefits.
    </p>
    <div class="pt-4">
      <a href="/online-appointments" class="inline-block bg-brand-700 text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-brand-900 transition-colors">
        Request a Free Consultation
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
